        <title type="html"><![CDATA[Learning Neural Light Fields with Ray-Space Embedding]]></title>
        <id>https://CDJ-happier.github.io/post/learning-neural-light-fields-with-ray-space-embedding/</id>
        <link href="https://CDJ-happier.github.io/post/learning-neural-light-fields-with-ray-space-embedding/">
        </link>
        <updated>2022-12-05T08:43:04.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文使用的是4D LF表达方式。可直接从(x,y,u,v)得到color+density，而不用像NeRF那样需要hundreds of sampled point。</p>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文使用的是4D LF表达方式。可直接从(x,y,u,v)得到color+density，而不用像NeRF那样需要hundreds of sampled point。</p>
]]></content>
