        <title type="html"><![CDATA[KeypointNeRF：3D head的重建]]></title>
        <id>https://CDJ-happier.github.io/post/keypointnerf3d-head-de-chong-jian/</id>
        <link href="https://CDJ-happier.github.io/post/keypointnerf3d-head-de-chong-jian/">
        </link>
        <updated>2022-11-23T08:23:44.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>KeypointNeRF: Generalizing Image-based Volumetric Avatars using Relative Spatial Encoding of Keypoints<br>
通过用3D关键点对query point进行相对空间编码，解决全局编码对细节重建不好的缺点；以及使用pixel-aligned feature实现细节重建。</p>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>KeypointNeRF: Generalizing Image-based Volumetric Avatars using Relative Spatial Encoding of Keypoints<br>
通过用3D关键点对query point进行相对空间编码，解决全局编码对细节重建不好的缺点；以及使用pixel-aligned feature实现细节重建。</p>
]]></content>
